00:01:54.762 --> 00:02:05.857
You all need to know this: they're going to use the drones. They're in sync and they're able to scan, hear noise, and see in infrared.

00:02:05.858 --> 00:02:13.170
You can't hide from them. The people who were left were trying to hide from these drones.

00:02:13.171 --> 00:02:19.718
This is very important. They're going to use them, and they fly all over the world.

00:02:19.719 --> 00:02:24.863
If you're left here, you need to know that you're not going to be able to run from this.

00:02:24.864 --> 00:02:36.620
The mark of the beast, the chip inside of you, communicates to the drone, and it's able to know if you have the mark or not.

00:02:36.621 --> 00:02:50.322
